# ERP Sales Analytics Pipeline

A Python data analytics project built on AdventureWorks ERP data.

## What it does
- Cleans and processes 31,000+ sales records
- Analyses revenue trends across 3 years (2011–2014)
- Identifies top customers by revenue
- Generates charts and a summary business report

## Tech Stack
- Python 3
- pandas
- matplotlib

## Project Structure
ERP suite/
├── data/                  # Raw and cleaned CSVs, output charts
├── src/
│   ├── clean_data.py      # Stage 2: Data cleaning
│   ├── analysis.py        # Stage 3: Business analysis
│   ├── visualise.py       # Stage 4: Charts
│   └── report.py          # Stage 5: Summary report
└── README.md